                            <comment id="16876536" author="githubbot" created="Mon, 1 Jul 2019 22:19:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;abbccdda commented on pull request #7021: &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-8620&quot; title=&quot;Race condition in StreamThread state change&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-8620&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-8620&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: fix stream task concurrent access issue&lt;br/&gt;
URL: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/7021&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/7021&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


